335
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:28,680
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ya.</b></font>

336
00:26:35,320 --> 00:26:38,160
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maka jangan beritahu Si untuk sekarang.</b></font>

337
00:26:39,120 --> 00:26:41,680
