00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:04,480
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

423
00:32:06,360 --> 00:32:07,520
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Kenapa kamu di sini?</b></font>

424
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:11,520
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aku sedang melintas dan mengira
