432
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:33,480
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Kamu tidak perlu khawatir.</b></font>

433
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:37,520
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Apa dia ingin minum bersama kita?</b></font>

434
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:40,680
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tidak. Dia tidak ikut.</b></font>

435
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:43,240
<font color="#ffff00"><b>- Ayo pergi.
- Sampai nanti.</b></font>

436
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,200
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Di mana Xiaoyou?</b></font>

437
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:02,000
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tunggu! Kenapa kamu tidak sabaran?</b></font>

438
00:33:02,080 --> 00:33:03,800
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aku mungkin sudah terlambat!</b></font>

439
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:05,800
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Kamu akan mematahkan tanganku.</b></font>

440
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,520
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Katakan padaku di mana Ximen dan Xiaoyou berada.</b></font>

441
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:10,120
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Kamar tidur utama. Pintu kedua di sebelah kiri.</b></font>

442
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:17,080
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Apa dia pikir dia wali Xiaoyou?</b></font>

443
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,080
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Dia sangat mudah ditipu.</b></font>

