452
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:28,840
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si dan Shancai akan
dikunci sepanjang malam.</b></font>

453
00:34:29,160 --> 00:34:31,040
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Apa gunanya berada di sana?</b></font>

454
00:34:32,120 --> 00:34:34,760
